description: Lists all services and authorized targets that the Amazon QuickSight IAM Identity Center application can access. This operation is only supported for Amazon QuickSight accounts that use IAM Identity Center.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contain the identity propagation configurations of.

nested_items.name: Services
nested_items.description: A list of services and their authorized targets that the Amazon QuickSight IAM Identity Center application can access.

nested_items.name: Service
nested_items.description: The name of the Amazon Web Services service.

nested_items.name: AuthorizedTargets
nested_items.description: Aist of authorized targets that are represented by IAM Identity Center application ARNs.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
